<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= application %> - Maintenance</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #212529;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .icon {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">ðŸ”§</div>
        <h1>Maintenance in Progress</h1>
        <p>We're currently performing scheduled maintenance on <%= application %>. We'll be back shortly.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your patience.</p>
        <div class="status">
            Expected completion: <%= maintenance_end_time || 'Soon' %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>